I get a similar lockup with this combo on 2.3.51:
 Driver: Promise Technology, Inc. 20262 (rev 01)   
 Disk:   Model=IBM-DPTA-353750, FwRev=P51OA30A, (4 disks total)
 MoBo:   Asus P2B
Works OK without DMA, the onboard PIIX4 works OK with DMA.
